org.cesecore.audit.enums

Enum EventTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EventTypes>
      • org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventTypes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<EventTypes>, org.cesecore.audit.enums.ConstantType<org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType>, org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType

    public enum EventTypes
extends java.lang.Enum<EventTypes>
implements org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType
    Contains all event types that CESeCore core needs to log to secure audit log. When doing secure audit log it is necessary to identify the event being logged.
    See Also:
    ModuleTypes, ServiceTypes
